# Molly Martinka
Sat, May 17
| 
West Hills Vineyards
Join us for an amazing evening with Molly Martinka live in our tasting room! Her enchanting voice and captivating performance will set the perfect tone as you enjoy our spring wines. It’s an unforgettable night of music and relaxation you won’t want to miss!
